      "span_text": "Bone marrow-derived macrophages were incubated with or without copper-oxidized human LDL at 100 g/mL for 48 hours. [CITATION_1] In additional experiments, murine red blood cells were used fresh or were artificially aged by Ca 2ϩ oxidation. 14 Fresh or oxidized red blood cells were incubated with murine macrophages, and apoptosis was assayed 24 hours later.",
